data.description: VA ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 2.75% ~ Classic Haymount Beauty, 4 bedrooms, 2 bath, hardwood floors up & downstairs, Large family room that flows to dining room, kitchen has updated stainless appliances & installed backsplash 2022,  Added 2nd pantry to kitchen,  Remodeled downstairs bath fall 2022 with tiled shower, upstairs has full bath & primary suite, Room for storage at double carport, painted house & replaced carport columns in 2021, Oil heat downstairs, heat pump upstairs. This is a walkable area of Haymount for riding bikes & being outside to go to coffee shops & restaurants!!
